            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/31/benz-smart1/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[EMMA]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 05:57:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[車壇動向]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[benz]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mercedes]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[smart]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1202246</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>由中國吉利控股及德國 Mercedes-Benz 集團合資經營的迷你車和微型車系列品牌 smart 近日在港舉行盛大的發佈會。由仁孚行擔任港澳地區的 <span lang="EN-US">smar<wbr />t </span>總經銷商，宣佈率先在港澳市場接受訂購的首款全新純電型號「smart #1」系列，首批發售版本包括「smart #1 BRABUS」以及「smart #1 Premium」，預計將於 2024 年首季正式交付。</p><p>Smart 表示，與高性能車製造商 BRABUS 聯乘推出的高性能版「smart #1 BRABU」，配備前後合共兩組高性能摩打，具 428 匹強大馬力及 543Nm 峯值扭力，靜止加速至時速 100 公里只需 3.9 秒，新車亦配合 AWD 全時四驅系統、跑車化底盤及懸掛系統。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202265" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06975-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06975-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06975-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06975-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06975-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06975-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202266" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN07108-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN07108-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN07108-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN07108-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN07108-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN07108-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202267" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2630-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2630-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2630-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2630-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2630-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2630-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202268" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2655-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2655-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2655-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2655-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2655-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2655-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202269" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2677-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2677-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2677-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2677-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2677-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2677-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>公司又指，smart #1 BRABUS 亦提供多種預設駕駛模式，例如選擇節能為主的 ECO 後驅模式，在 WLTP 模式下的最長續航距離便提升至 400 公里。</p><p>「smart #1 BRABUS」車身配備專屬的車體擾流組件，例如前、後包圍、車側裙腳及車頂尾翼、又有 19 吋 Dynamo 合金輪圈及鮮紅色塗層制動卡鉗。車廂內則以 Alcantara 物料覆蓋外層的三幅式軚環、跑車式加速及制動腳踏板、配色對比強烈的 BRABUS 跑車桶型座椅、像真程度極高的模擬引擎音效系統，以及由音響品牌 Beats Audio 專責主理及設定的 13 聲道高級音響。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202271 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2736-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2736-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2736-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2736-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2736-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2736-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202270 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2735-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2735-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2735-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2735-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2735-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2735-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>採用全新設計風格的「smart #1 Premium」車頭及車尾配備 CyberSparks+智能 LED 頭燈、19 吋合金輪圈、Portal Door 新型車門、「Halo roof」天幕式玻璃車頂。車身長闊高為 4,270×1,822×1,636mm，軸距達 2,750mm，車內空間非常寬敞，而懸浮式車頂及車身設有多種色調配搭，可供車主根據個人喜好自訂組合。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202248" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06925-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06925-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06925-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06925-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06925-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06925-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202259" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2682-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2682-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2682-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2682-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2682-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2682-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />  <img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202261" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2688-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2688-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2688-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2688-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2688-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2688-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202262" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2703-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2703-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2703-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2703-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2703-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2703-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>而車內的前座可作 6 方位電動調校，採用全車多媒體及輔助系統操作中樞的 12.8 吋輕觸式大型 LED 顯示熒幕、Beats 13 聲道揚聲器系統，以及對應 Apple Carplay 和 Android Auto。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202263 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2704-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2704-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2704-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2704-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2704-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2704-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202250 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06942-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06942-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06942-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06942-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06942-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06942-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: left;">「smart #1 Premium」採用 RWD 後輪驅動設計，具 272 匹馬力及 343Nm 峯值扭力，在靜止加速至時速 100 公里下需 6.7 秒，WLTP 模式下有長達 440 公里的最長續航距，足以應付日常用車需要。另外，smart 亦將車側睹後鏡盲點偵測顯示（BSD）、車前（FCTA）及車後（RCTA）橫越預警系統、 行車線輔助系統（LKA）、360 度鳥瞰式監察鏡頭、設有自動停車及開行功能的主動巡航系統 （ACC）、自動泊車輔助系統（APA）等主被動行車安全數碼系統加入新車中。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202247 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06921-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06921-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06921-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06921-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06921-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06921-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>兩款 smart #1 型號於 11 月 1 日起在 smart showroon 舉行優先預覽，有興趣者可於網上預約參觀。另外，全新的 smart 香港官方網頁（hk.smart.com）亦同時開於，接收買家於網上預訂及創造個人化「smart #1」。</p><p>首批「smart #1 BRABUS」及「smart #1 Premium」買家可享早鳥優惠預訂新車，售價分別由 HK$339,000 及$299,000 起。首批新車將於 2024 年第一季正式交付，以配合明年 3 月底屆滿的電動車「一換一」首次登記税寬減安排。</p><p>資料來源：smart</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
